COMPETITION FOR A CAUSE 🤍

I have decided to partner with @shelterforlombokdogs + @novotellombokresortandvillas + @sikaralombokhotel to help support and improve the situation and lives of the dogs in Lombok, Indonesia. 
There are severe animal rights issues and abuse island-wide. As an animal lover I couldn’t ignore the pain, fear, and unnecessary suffering. Disaster recently hit the shelter with heavy rains that flooded the land so they had to evacuate their 31 puppies and adults in current care. They built a temporary shelter but, they desperately need to relocate. There are thousands of starving dogs on the streets, puppies being dumped or killed, and stray dogs with horrible wounds that eminently lead to death when untreated. Due to the lack of food, these dogs have to fight for survival everyday and suffer slow agonizing deaths. Very few dogs in Lombok are sterilized and yet majority of their puppies don’t make it because they die of starvation. They need your help of generous donations to make their dream for the dogs and puppies of Lombok come true.

HOW TO ENTER:
Please make a minimum donation of $25 USD directly to their gofundme page.

https://www.gofundme.com/f/shelter-for-lombok-dogs

WHAT YOU HAVE A CHANCE TO WIN: 
-2 Economy Flights To Lombok, Indonesia
-Free Airport Pick Up + Drop Off
-Complimentary Stay At A Private Pool Villa For 2 Nights At The Novotel Lombok Resort (Breakfast Included)
-2X Complimentary 60 Minute Massages 
-Complimentary Stay At Sikara Hotel For 2 Nights (Breakfast Included)
-Transfer Between The Two Hotels
-Yoga Class With The Puppies

TERMS AND CONDITIONS:
-The winner must submit at least 2 possible stay periods for both general managers to check availability to redeem the offer.
-Villa/Room suitable for 2 adults & 1 child maximum 
-Should someone win, that has a core family bigger than that 2 adults + 1 child individual solutions will have to be looked into.
-Valid for a stay before 22.12.2023
-Not during July & August (Peak Season)
-Not during Events (major public holidays, MotoGP & other events at the circuit)
-Subject to availability
-Winner will be selected April 1, 2023 with proof of donation
